{"tid":664331,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！雲加續約阿仙奴兩年","createTime":"2018-05-14T04:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T05:52:18.000Z","uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d0baf515c71b3b35bb0b4678a633f7a67b03a063","tid":664331,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=BzsFvvO4moS6CNL1%2FM7kiC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=564f482a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】BBC報道，阿仙奴與法國籍領隊雲加續約兩年，這消息其後獲官方證實。<br />\n<br />\n於本季後約滿的雲加於周一與球會班主高安基會面，並於昨日與球會董事局成員傾談後，已作好留任的共識。BBC稱雙方剛在球會簽約，預計官方很快正式公佈。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴本季戰績未如理想，只能以第5名成績完成，是雲加自1996年領「兵」以來首次聯賽前4名不入，錯失參與來季歐洲資格，亦是其任內首次排名在倫敦死敵熱刺之下。<br />\n<br />\n不過，阿仙奴上周末在足總盃決賽以2:1力克聯賽冠軍，本季不致無錦標落袋，同時粉碎銳氣正盛的車路士的雙冠美夢。"},{"pid":"0adc658d58d3dad67065e3665b8c6891d9795b7e","tid":664331,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/200120_7f4f46f743a45b46870a2fb1ce639698.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F200120_7f4f46f743a45b46870a2fb1ce639698.gif&h=f0a06d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先有冇人煲衲？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/424503/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/424503/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}